camSetDir 
Behavior: local 
Game: Operation Flashpoint (1.00) 
Description: Set the direction of the given camera.Needs the call of camCommit 
 to be conducted.  
Syntax:  
 camera camSetDir direction 
Parameters: 
camera: Object - object of type "camera" 
direction: Number - direction in degrees, range 0 to 360 
Return Value: 
 Nothing